            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收跌71點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收報7.1167，較上日官方收盤價跌71點，較上日夜盤收盤跌32點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15442425-%e5%9c%a8%e5%b2%b8%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3%e5%85%8c%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c71%e9%bb%9e-2",
